<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Ahmed Almadhoun, Transport Engineer & Researcher</title>
<meta name="description" content="Transport Engineer and PhD Researcher focused on freight systems, accessibility, and infrastructure.">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;1,9..144,300;1,9..144,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --bg:#2b2926;
  --surface:#333028;
  --surface2:#3a362d;
  --border:#4a453b;
  --border-light:#423e35;
  --text:#f0ebe2;
  --muted:#9a9085;
  --faint:#6a6158;
  --accent:#c48a42;
  --accent-mid:#ad7336;
  --accent-light:#3a2816;
  --max:1120px;
  --sans:'Inter',system-ui,sans-serif;
  --serif:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;
}
body.dark-mode nav{background:rgba(26,29,36,0.92);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04)}
body.dark-mode{
  --bg:#1a1d24;
  --surface:#20232d;
  --surface2:#262a35;
  --border:#353a48;
  --border-light:#2e3340;
  --text:#e8e4d9;
  --muted:#8a8fa0;
  --faint:#555c6e;
  --accent:#d4924a;
  --accent-mid:#c07e38;
  --accent-light:#2a2010;
}
#theme-btn{position:fixed;bottom:28px;right:28px;z-index:200;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--muted);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:9px 16px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .25s;opacity:.72}
#theme-btn:hover{color:var(--text);border-color:var(--border-light);opacity:1}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:16px}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:400;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}
nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(43,41,38,0.94);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);padding:0 40px}
.nav-inner{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:56px}
.nav-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:17px;font-weight:400;color:var(--text);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px;list-:none}
.nav-links a{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.01em;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.wrap{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px}
#hero{padding:100px 40px 96px;max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto}
.hero-location{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.13em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:28px}
.hero-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(54px,7.5vw,94px);font-weight:300;line-height:.97;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:6px}
.hero-micro{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:18px}
.hero-sub{font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,20px);font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;color:var(--text);max-width:560px;margin-bottom:14px;opacity:.92}
.hero-body{font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--muted);max-width:500px;margin-bottom:36px}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:22px}
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:11px 22px;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:500;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px;transition:all .2s;cursor:pointer;border:none;font-family:var(--sans);letter-spacing:0.01em}
.btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:#1a1714}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--accent-mid)}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--text);border:1.5px solid var(--border)}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.btn-cv{background:transparent;color:var(--faint);border:1.5px solid var(--border-light);opacity:.5}
.btn-cv:hover{opacity:1;color:var(--text);border-color:var(--border)}
.hero-cred{font-size:12px;color:var(--faint);letter-spacing:0.01em}
.section{padding:84px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.section-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:10px}
.section-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(26px,3.8vw,38px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:36px;opacity:.92}
#what{background:var(--surface)}
.what-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:52px;align-items:start}
.what-text p{font-size:17px;line-height:1.82;color:var(--muted)}
.what-pills{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px}
.pill-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;padding:16px 18px;background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;transition:border-color .25s,background .25s}
.pill-item:hover{background:var(--surface2);border-color:var(--border)}
.pill-dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:6px}
.pill-text{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:3px}
.pill-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
#research{background:var(--bg)}
.research-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.r-card{padding:32px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-light);display:block;transition:background .3s ease,box-shadow .3s ease}
.r-card:first-child{border-top:1px solid var(--border-light)}
.r-card:hover{background:var(--surface);box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.03)}
.r-num{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:9px;font-family:var(--sans)}
.r-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:21px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.25;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:9px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;cursor:pointer;transition:color .2s;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:baseline;gap:12px}
.r-title:hover{color:var(--accent)}
.r-toggle{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:16px;font-weight:300;color:var(--faint);flex-shrink:0;transition:transform .25s ease,color .25s ease;line-height:1}
.r-card.open .r-toggle{transform:rotate(45deg);color:var(--accent)}
.r-abstract{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;margin-top:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--muted);border-left:2px solid var(--border);padding-left:14px;transition:max-height .4s ease,margin-top .3s ease,opacity .3s ease;opacity:0}
.r-card.open .r-abstract{max-height:600px;margin-top:14px;opacity:1}
.r-tags{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px;margin-top:14px}
.r-tag{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.05em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 9px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent)}
.r-link{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;border-bottom:1px solid transparent;transition:border-color .2s}
.r-link:hover{border-color:var(--accent)}
.r-link svg{width:11px;height:11px}
.r-meta{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--faint);text-align:left;margin-top:14px;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.01em}
#photography{background:var(--surface)}
.photo-intro{font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--muted);max-width:520px;margin-bottom:28px;margin-top:-12px}
.photo-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:3px}
.photo-cell{overflow:hidden;position:relative;cursor:pointer;background:var(--surface2)}
.photo-cell img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;transition:transform .55s ease,filter .4s ease;filter:saturate(.92) brightness(.95) contrast(1.04)}
.photo-cell:hover img{transform:scale(1.04);filter:saturate(.98) brightness(1)}
.photo-cell:nth-child(1){aspect-ratio:8/5;grid-column:span 2}
.photo-cell:nth-child(2){aspect-ratio:4/5}
.photo-cell:nth-child(3){aspect-ratio:4/3}
.photo-cell:nth-child(4){aspect-ratio:8/5;grid-column:span 2}
.photo-caption{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:28px 14px 12px;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.72),transparent);opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
.photo-cell:hover .photo-caption{opacity:1}
.photo-caption span{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85)}
.photo-footer{margin-top:24px;display:flex;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.photo-footer a{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none}
.photo-footer a:hover{text-decoration:underline}
#about{background:var(--bg)}
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start}
.about-text p{font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.85;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:20px}
.about-text p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.about-facts{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.fact{padding:16px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.fact:first-child{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.fact-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:4px}
.fact-value{font-size:14.5px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px}
.fact-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
#thoughts{background:var(--surface)}
.thoughts-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:2px}
.t-card{background:var(--bg);padding:28px 24px;cursor:pointer;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:background .25s}
.t-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--accent);transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .35s}
.t-card:hover{background:var(--surface2)}
.t-card:hover::after{transform:scaleX(1)}
.t-date{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:12px}
.t-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:20px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.25;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:10px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.t-excerpt{font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--muted)}
.t-cat{display:inline-block;margin-top:16px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent)}
#post-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:600;background:#1c1a17;display:none;flex-direction:column;overflow-y:auto;cursor:default;opacity:0;transition:opacity .35s}
#post-overlay.open{display:flex}
#post-overlay.visible{opacity:1}
.post-curtain{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:var(--accent);transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform .9s ease;z-index:601}
#post-overlay.visible .post-curtain{transform:scaleX(1)}
.post-inner{max-width:660px;margin:0 auto;padding:100px 40px 80px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s ease .3s,transform .6s ease .3s}
#post-overlay.visible .post-inner{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
.post-meta{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(201,149,90,0.5);margin-bottom:36px;display:flex;gap:20px}
.post-heading{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(34px,5.5vw,60px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.025em;color:#ede8df;margin-bottom:36px}
.post-rule{width:36px;height:1px;background:rgba(201,149,90,0.4);margin-bottom:40px}
.post-body{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.9;color:rgba(237,232,223,0.68)}
.post-body p{margin-bottom:24px}
.post-close{position:fixed;top:28px;right:36px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(237,232,223,0.3);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:color .2s;z-index:602}
.post-close:hover{color:rgba(237,232,223,.8)}
footer{padding:36px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface2)}
.footer-inner{max-width:var(--max);margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px}
.footer-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:17px;font-weight:300;color:var(--text)}
.footer-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--faint);margin-top:3px}
.footer-links{display:flex;gap:20px}
.footer-links a{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
#lb{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(4,3,2,0.97);backdrop-filter:blur(2px);z-index:1000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:zoom-out;opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}
#lb.open{display:flex}
#lb.visible{opacity:1}
#lb img{max-width:90vw;max-height:90vh;object-fit:contain}
#lb-close{position:absolute;top:24px;right:32px;background:none;border:none;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:500;transition:color .2s}
#lb-close:hover{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85)}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);transition:opacity .75s ease,transform .75s ease}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
@media(max-width:768px){
  nav{padding:0 20px}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  #hero{padding:64px 20px 56px}
  .wrap{padding:0 20px}
  .section{padding:56px 0}
  .what-grid,.about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:32px}
  .photo-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  .photo-cell:nth-child(1),.photo-cell:nth-child(4){grid-column:span 1;aspect-ratio:4/3}
  .photo-cell:nth-child(2){aspect-ratio:4/3}
  footer{padding:28px 20px}
  .footer-inner{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
}
#contact{background:var(--surface)}
.contact-form{max-width:580px}
.cf-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px}
.cf-field{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;margin-bottom:16px}
.cf-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint)}
.cf-input,.cf-textarea{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:14px;padding:13px 16px;border-radius:5px;outline:none;transition:border-color .25s,background .25s;resize:none;width:100%}
.cf-input:focus,.cf-textarea:focus{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--surface2)}
.cf-input::placeholder,.cf-textarea::placeholder{color:var(--faint)}
.cf-success{display:none;margin-top:24px;padding:16px 20px;border-left:2px solid var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
@media(max-width:768px){.cf-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
/* === FEATURE 1: Typed animation === */
.typed-cursor{display:inline-block;width:2px;height:12px;background:var(--accent);margin-left:2px;vertical-align:middle;animation:blink .75s step-end infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}

/* === FEATURE 2: Timeline === */
#timeline{background:var(--bg)}
.tl-wrap{position:relative;max-width:700px}
.tl-line{position:absolute;left:18px;top:0;bottom:0;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,var(--border) 60px,var(--border) calc(100% - 60px),transparent);opacity:.5}
.tl-item{position:relative;padding:0 0 52px 56px;opacity:0;transform:translateX(-12px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
.tl-item.tl-visible{opacity:1;transform:translateX(0)}
.tl-dot{position:absolute;left:10px;top:4px;width:17px;height:17px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--bg);border:1.5px solid var(--border);transition:border-color .3s,background .3s}
.tl-item:hover .tl-dot{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light)}
.tl-item.tl-active .tl-dot{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--accent-light)}
.tl-year{font-size:10.5px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:6px;opacity:.8}
.tl-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:19px;font-weight:300;color:var(--text);line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:6px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.tl-sub{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65}
.tl-tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:10px;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.07em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--accent-light);color:var(--accent)}
.tl-item:last-child{padding-bottom:0}

/* === FEATURE 3: Map === */
#map-section{background:var(--surface)}
.map-container{position:relative;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border)}
#corridor-map{width:100%;height:480px;background:var(--bg)}
.map-legend{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;margin-top:18px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.legend-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}
.map-tooltip{position:absolute;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:14px 16px;pointer-events:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s;z-index:10;max-width:240px}
.map-tooltip.visible{opacity:1}
.tt-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px;font-family:var(--serif)}
.tt-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:4px}
.tt-val{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
.tt-fap{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;margin-top:8px;padding-top:8px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.tt-fap.high{color:#e07060}
.tt-fap.mid{color:#c48a42}
.tt-fap.low{color:#6aaa7a}
.map-stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:20px}
.mstat{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:14px 16px}
.mstat-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--faint);margin-bottom:6px}
.mstat-val{font-size:22px;font-weight:300;font-family:var(--serif);color:var(--text)}
.mstat-sub{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
@media(max-width:768px){
  #corridor-map{height:320px}
  .map-stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .map-legend{gap:14px}
}
.tl-item.tl-ongoing .tl-dot{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-light);animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(196,138,66,0.4)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 0 6px rgba(196,138,66,0)}}
.tl-item.tl-ongoing .tl-tag{position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.tl-item.tl-ongoing .tl-tag::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:-100%;width:100%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(196,138,66,0.3),transparent);animation:shimmer 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes shimmer{0%{left:-100%}100%{left:100%}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#hero" class="nav-name">Ahmed Almadhoun</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#research">Research</a></li>
      <li><a href="#photography">Photography</a></li>
      <li><a href="#thoughts">Thoughts</a></li>
      <li><a href="#timeline">Journey</a></li>
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<div id="hero">
  <div class="hero-location">Warsaw, Poland</div>
  <h1 class="hero-name">Ahmed<br>Almadhoun</h1>
  <p class="hero-micro"><span id="typed-text"></span><span class="typed-cursor"></span></p>
  <p class="hero-sub">Transport Engineer and PhD Researcher focused on freight systems, accessibility, and real-world infrastructure performance.</p>
  <p class="hero-body">I study how transport infrastructure shapes economic access, especially in freight systems that most people depend on but rarely notice.</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="#research" class="btn btn-primary">View Research</a>
    <a href="#photography" class="btn btn-outline">Photography</a>
  </div>
  <p class="hero-cred">Published research, simulation models, and real-world infrastructure analysis.</p>
</div>

<section id="what" class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-label">What I Do</div>
    </div>
    <div class="what-grid reveal">
      <div class="what-text">
        <p>I work on understanding how infrastructure limitations affect freight movement and economic connectivity. My work combines simulation, data analysis, and real-world transport systems to identify inefficiencies and improve accessibility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="what-pills">
        <div class="pill-item">
          <div class="pill-dot"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="pill-text">Freight Accessibility</div>
            <div class="pill-sub">Measuring how logistics networks connect regions, corridors, and economic activity.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pill-item">
          <div class="pill-dot"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="pill-text">Transport Simulation</div>
            <div class="pill-sub">Using modelling and data analysis to test infrastructure performance and alternatives.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pill-item">
          <div class="pill-dot"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="pill-text">Infrastructure Equity</div>
            <div class="pill-sub">Understanding where transport systems create hidden disadvantages and uneven access.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
